updated_cases.title: Verify whether the SSL Decryption policies affected by the custom categories which the URL belongs to are displayed
updated_cases.custom_summary: Verify whether the SSL Decryption policies affected by the custom categories which the URL belongs to are displayed
updated_cases.custom_steps:
1. Login to Tenant WebUI
 2. Click on Web, under Profiles in Policies tab
 3. Click on URL Lookup
 4. Under URL Lookup, enter any URL and hit Enter
updated_cases.custom_expected:
1. In URL List search result, Site Name should be seen first and then the domain.
 2. The SSL Decryption Policy names should be displayed. 
 3. Steering Configuration tooltip should not be seen
